formula: Expansion of ( theta_2(q)^16 + theta_3(q)^16 + theta_4(q)^16 + 30 * theta_2(q)^8 * theta_3(q)^8 ) / 2 in powers of q. - [Conway and Sloane]Expansion of E_4(q^2)^2 + (E_4(q) - E_4(q^2))^2 / 15 in powers of q. - _Michael Somos_, Nov 29 2007Expansion of ( eta(q)^48 + 32 * eta(q)^24 * eta(q^2)^24 + 4096 * eta(q^2)^48 ) / ( eta(q) * eta(q^2) )^16 in powers of q. - _Michael Somos_, Nov 29 2007G.f. is Fourier series of a weight 8 level 2 modular form. f(-1 / (2 t)) = 16 (t/i)^8 f(t) where q = exp(2 Pi i t). - _Michael Somos_, Nov 29 2007
